  "subject": "chore: pin fixed ingest digest; widen kind CronWorkflow schedules",
  "body": "Digest bump for 1a73df7's two-phase retention-pass fix. CI run 29196867242,\nverified resolvable via the GHCR registry API.\n\nAlso widens kind's ingest CronWorkflow schedules from */15 and */20 to\nevery 6h: at */15 the schedule auto-fired mid-verification (Task 4's own\nacceptance run caught this), racing the manual before/after retention\ncheck against a concurrent auto-triggered run on the same fixture data.\nconcurrencyPolicy: Forbid only guards CronWorkflow-scheduled runs against\neach other, not against a manually kubectl-created Workflow.\n"
}
